"There is not only my freedom, but the freedom of all Turkey. I'm glad our people are acting to claim it. I thank everyone for affection and solidarity, your courage makes me happy," Imamoglu said. The mayor of Istanbul also thanked the citizens who yesterday went to vote for it at the primary, choosing it as a challenger of the President-in-Office Recep Tayip Erdogan> for the presidential elections of 2028.
